User Stories
1.	As the Solo Traveler, I need to be able to track all of my upcoming trips, so that I can be sure not to miss any of my reservations.

2.	As the Solo Traveler, I need to be able to see all of my past trips which I have taken, so that I can provide that info to my parents so they know I am not wasting their money.

3.	As the Solo Traveler, I need to be able to change a reservation on short notice, so that if I decide to stay somewhere longer that wont be a problem.
